description:
Decoy - Menagerie, Part 2 (2006) (Digital) (DR & Quinch-Empire)


Decoy: Menagerie, Part 2 features over 100 full-color pages of stories by Eisner Award-winning writers and artists, as well as newcomers frothing at the bit to share remarkable talent with the comics world. Showcases such talents as Ty Templeton, Mike Kunkel, Brian Wood, Azad Injejikian, Ryan Woodward, Phil Hester, and Mr. Decoy himself, Courtney Huddleston
